            "y": 685,
            "width": 230,
            "height": 150,
            "text": "A2A = Horizontal interop\nAgent ←→ Agent\n(task delegation, collaboration)\n\nMCP = Vertical interop\nAgent ←→ Tools & Data\n(tool calls, resource access)\n\nTogether they form a complete\necosystem for agentic AI.",
